---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Curriculum Vitae" currentPath="/cv/">
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 px-6 md:px-12 max-w-[1000px] mx-auto min-h-screen">
    
    <!-- Headline Section -->
    <div class="mb-20">
      <span class="text-xs tracking-[0.3em] font-bold text-primary uppercase block mb-4">DOCUMENT : CV_01</span>
      <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black tracking-tighter leading-none mb-6">CURRICULUM<br/>VITAE</h1>
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 mt-12 pt-12 border-t border-on-surface/10">
        <div class="md:w-1/3">
          <h2 class="text-sm tracking-widest font-bold uppercase text-on-surface-variant">Profile Abstract</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-2/3 space-y-6 text-on-surface text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            With over a decade of experience in software engineering, I have navigated complex technical landscapes across aerospace, defense, healthcare, and semiconductor industries. My career is defined by a commitment to safety-critical systems, robust architectural design, and mission-critical software development.
          </p>
          <p>
            Currently, I am deeply interested in pivoting my career towards AI-centric domains. I am actively pursuing both professional and personal projects involving machine learning and deep learning, aiming to integrate my background in systems architecture with the latest advancements in artificial intelligence.
          </p>
          <div>
            <span class="font-bold block mb-2">Core Competencies:</span>
            <ul class="list-none space-y-1 pl-4 border-l-2 border-primary/30">
              <li>· Avionics (e.g. IFF Transponder, CVDR)</li>
              <li>· High and low-level software development in Safety Critical Systems (e.g. Bootloader, BSP&IO Drivers, Application Level)</li>
              <li>· Graphical User Interface development (e.g. Qt, Scade Suite, VAPS XT, .NET)</li>
              <li>· Software Development Life-cycle Methodologies (e.g. Agile, Waterfall, V-Model)</li>
              <li>· Machine Learning Applications (e.g. Neural Networks, Tensorflow, Keras API)</li>
              <li>· Embedded Software Development (e.g. Lithography & Aerospace domains)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Experience Section -->
    <div class="mb-20">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-12">
        <div class="h-px bg-on-surface/10 grow"></div>
        <h2 class="text-sm tracking-widest font-bold uppercase text-on-surface-variant">Professional Experience</h2>
        <div class="h-px bg-on-surface/10 grow"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-16">
        <!-- ASML -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 group">
          <div class="md:col-span-3">
            <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-primary">09.2023 — PRESENT</span>
          </div>
          <div class="md:col-span-9">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight mb-1">Software Engineer</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant font-medium mb-4">ASML</p>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-on-surface/80">
              Development & Engineering, MX Exposure Imaging, DUV Image Align Software. Continued execution of responsibilities established during my YER contract, converted to ASML payroll. Implementations in C, Python and Julia languages. Acted as Scrum Master.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ASML (YER) -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 group">
          <div class="md:col-span-3">
            <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-primary opacity-60">07.2022 — 09.2023</span>
          </div>
          <div class="md:col-span-9">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight mb-1">Software Engineer</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant font-medium mb-4">ASML (on behalf of YER Nederland B.V.)</p>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-on-surface/80 mb-2">
              Development & Engineering, MX Exposure Imaging, DUV Image Align Software.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-none space-y-1 pl-4 border-l border-on-surface/20 text-sm text-on-surface/80">
              <li>· Implementations in C, Python and Julia languages.</li>
              <li>· Scrum Master roles.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ICTerra -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 group">
          <div class="md:col-span-3">
            <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-primary opacity-60">11.2021 — 06.2022</span>
          </div>
          <div class="md:col-span-9">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight mb-1">MIDAS Team Lead & Software Architect</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant font-medium mb-4">ICterra</p>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-on-surface/80 mb-2">
              MIDAS: Early Diagnosis, Evaluation and Tracking System for Breast Cancer. An R&D project (funded by Tubitak) detecting malignant breast sections in mammogram images in collaboration with Hacettepe University Hospital.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-none space-y-1 pl-4 border-l border-on-surface/20 text-sm text-on-surface/80 mb-4">
              <li>· Development and training of the multi-stage (Abnormality + BIRADS) neural network classifier on a multi-view, multi-class, imbalanced dataset.</li>
              <li>· Implementing a dockerized, remote working infrastructure.</li>
              <li>· Utilization of training runs on the remote, multi-GPU, unix-based workstation environment.</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant">
              Additional role: Managed MXRAY (Mobile Digital XRAY System) firmware maintenance for Aselsan, on behalf of ICterra.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Turkish Aerospace (IMODE Lead) -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 group">
          <div class="md:col-span-3">
            <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-primary opacity-60">01.2020 — 11.2021</span>
          </div>
          <div class="md:col-span-9">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight mb-1">IMODE Team Lead</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant font-medium mb-4">Turkish Aerospace</p>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-on-surface/80 mb-2">
              IMODE, Kit Development. Maintenance of the current tool and developing additional features including ARINC 661 Toolkit, Architecture Design Toolkit (AADL), Tool Qualification Kit (reg. DO standards), and Software Development Kit.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-none space-y-1 pl-4 border-l border-on-surface/20 text-sm text-on-surface/80">
              <li>· Scrum Master, Sprint Planning.</li>
              <li>· Researching new technologies and standards, identifying challenging topics and risks.</li>
              <li>· Co-instructor at Model-Based Design lecture at Yildiz Technical University Avionics Engineering master's programme.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Turkish Aerospace (Senior SDE) -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 group">
          <div class="md:col-span-3">
            <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-primary opacity-60">03.2019 — 01.2020</span>
          </div>
          <div class="md:col-span-9">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight mb-1">Senior Software Design Engineer</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant font-medium mb-4">Turkish Aerospace</p>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-on-surface/80 mb-2">
              IMODE: Integrated Model-Based Design & Development Environment. Developed as a competition to VAPS and SCADE (Suite). Implemented in C++ with Qt Framework.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-none space-y-1 pl-4 border-l border-on-surface/20 text-sm text-on-surface/80">
              <li>· Development of plans, standards, design, requirements and source code.</li>
              <li>· Participated in Project & Model Management (incl. File IO module).</li>
              <li>· Template-Based, multilingual Code Generator (incl. C, C++ and Python Language templates).</li>
              <li>· License Management (Public Key Authentication).</li>
              <li>· Graphical and logical model designs for Advanced Jet Trainer and Light Attack Aircraft, PVI (Pilot Vehicle Interface) Development project.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Aselsan -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 group">
          <div class="md:col-span-3">
            <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-primary opacity-60">08.2017 — 03.2019</span>
          </div>
          <div class="md:col-span-9">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight mb-1">Software Design Engineer</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant font-medium mb-4">Aselsan <span class="text-xs font-normal opacity-80">(on behalf of Turkish Aerospace)</span></p>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-on-surface/80 mb-2">
              New Generation Trainer Aircraft, OFP Development. Implemented in C++ using IBM Rational Rhapsody. Supported verification activities.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-none space-y-1 pl-4 border-l border-on-surface/20 text-sm text-on-surface/80">
              <li>· IFF (Identification Friend or Foe) Transponder.</li>
              <li>· CVRFDR (Cockpit Voice (CVR) and Flight Data (FDR) Recorder).</li>
              <li>· Initial development of some radar pages using VAPS.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Turkish Aerospace (SDE) -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 group">
          <div class="md:col-span-3">
            <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-primary opacity-60">08.2016 — 08.2017</span>
          </div>
          <div class="md:col-span-9">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight mb-1">Software Design Engineer</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant font-medium mb-4">Turkish Aerospace</p>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-on-surface/80">
              <span class="font-bold underline decoration-primary underline-offset-4">New Gen Trainer Aircraft, LRU Firmware:</span> Development of source code for Bootloader and I2C Device Driver for Symbol Generator (SG) and Rudder Assistant System (RAS) hardwares. Implemented in C.<br/><br/>
              <span class="font-bold underline decoration-primary underline-offset-4">Military Transport Aircraft, Avionics Modernization:</span> Development of an ARINC 429 data simulator tool for the verification environment using .NET Framework in C#.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- AYESAŞ -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 group">
          <div class="md:col-span-3">
            <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-primary opacity-60">08.2014 — 08.2016</span>
          </div>
          <div class="md:col-span-9">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight mb-1">Software Engineer</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant font-medium mb-4">AYESAŞ</p>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-on-surface/80">
              <span class="font-bold underline decoration-primary underline-offset-4">New Gen Trainer Aircraft, LRU Firmware:</span> Development of requirements using IBM Rational DOORS for Intercommunication System (ICS), Multi-Function Display (MFD), and Keyboard/Cockpit Display Unit (KDU/CDU).<br/><br/>
              <span class="font-bold underline decoration-primary underline-offset-4">MALE class Unmanned Aerial Vehicle, BSP & IO Drivers:</span> Development of plans, standards, design, requirements and source code for Bootloader, Dataloader, and BSP & IO Device Drivers (Ethernet, Serial, Flash, NVRAM) implemented in C and Assembly.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Bilişim AŞ -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 group">
          <div class="md:col-span-3">
            <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-primary opacity-60">06.2013 — 08.2014</span>
          </div>
          <div class="md:col-span-9">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight mb-1">Software Engineer</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant font-medium mb-4">Bilişim AŞ</p>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-on-surface/80">
              <span class="font-bold underline decoration-primary underline-offset-4">DGCA Information Administration System:</span> Development, maintenance and support using Java Server Faces.<br/><br/>
              <span class="font-bold underline decoration-primary underline-offset-4">Business Intelligence Application:</span> Development using PHP, Java and Javascript. Multiple DB management systems used (OracleDB, MySQL, MsSQL).
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Dual Columns: Education & Certifications -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
      <!-- Education -->
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-sm tracking-widest font-bold uppercase text-on-surface-variant">Education</h2>
          <div class="h-px bg-on-surface/10 grow"></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-primary opacity-60 mb-1 block">2016 — 2019</span>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-1">MSc. Multimedia Computing</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant font-medium mb-2 text-sm">Middle East Technical University</p>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-on-surface/80">
              Courses: Signal Processing, Machine Learning, Motion Capture, Speech Recognition, Image Processing, Deep Learning. Used Python for development.<br/>
              <span class="italic text-xs mt-2 block opacity-80">Thesis: Speaker and Posture Classification using Instantaneous Acoustic Features of Breath Signals</span>
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-primary opacity-60 mb-1 block">2009 — 2013</span>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-1">BSc. Computer Engineering</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant font-medium mb-2 text-sm">Hacettepe University</p>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-on-surface/80">
              Focus: Operating Systems, Data Structures and Algorithms, Software Design Patterns.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Publications -->
        <div class="mt-12">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-sm tracking-widest font-bold uppercase text-on-surface-variant">Publications</h2>
            <div class="h-px bg-on-surface/10 grow"></div>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="text-sm">
              <span class="font-bold">Speaker and Posture Classification using Instantaneous Intraspeech Breathing Features</span><br/>
              <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2005.12230" class="text-primary hover:underline" target="_blank">arXiv:2005.12230 (2020)</a>
            </li>
            <li class="text-sm">
              <span class="font-bold">BreathBase: Intra-Speech Breathing Dataset</span><br/>
              <a href="https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3841039" class="text-primary hover:underline" target="_blank">10.5281/zenodo.3841039 (2020)</a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Certifications -->
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-sm tracking-widest font-bold uppercase text-on-surface-variant">Certifications & Exam Scores</h2>
          <div class="h-px bg-on-surface/10 grow"></div>
        </div>
        
        <ul class="space-y-6">
          <li class="flex justify-between border-b border-on-surface/5 pb-2">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold">Deep Learning Fundamentals</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant text-right">NVIDIA DLI (2017)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between border-b border-on-surface/5 pb-2">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold">ALES: 83</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant text-right">Equiv. GRE: 157 (2016)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between border-b border-on-surface/5 pb-2">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold">YDS: 95</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant text-right">Equiv. TOEFL-IBT: 114 (2016)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between border-b border-on-surface/5 pb-2">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold">DO-178C Short Courses</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant text-right">AFuzion Inc (2015)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between border-b border-on-surface/5 pb-2">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold">Using DOORS for Requirement Mgmt.</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant text-right">PROYA (2015)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between border-b border-on-surface/5 pb-2">
            <span class="text-sm font-bold">Integrity BSP & IO Drivers</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant text-right">Green Hills Software (2014)</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
